   ``He's a real person,'' said John Surmay, who in 24 years in
Elizabeth has seen only one mayor. ``In this plastic world we live
in, he's not plastic, phony or shallow, and he's not a wimp. He's
made a lot of decisions and is ready to back up every one of them.''
