at 155.72. On the American Stock Exchange, the market value index
was unchanged at 306.01. On Friday, the Dow Jones industrial average
lost 14.11 points to close at 2,168.57. That left the market's
best-known barometer with a decline of 0.36 for the week, but a gain
of 229.74 points, or 11.85 percent, for the year.
